722978f-a.title: Manhattan: Rivington Street - Eldridge Street
722978f-a.text:
56 to 64 Rivington Street, north side, east from but not including
Eldridge, to but not including Allen Streets, showing the Warshauer First
Congregation Synagogue (No. 58-60). The congregation was organized in
1889 and conducts services in Hebrew
1NAN.  NV6e: 25  July 23, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
